author: MTV News Staff
title: Young Doctors and Nurses Feel Like ‘Soldiers Going Into Battle’ Amid Coronavirus Pandemic
description: As the number of COVID-19 cases in the U.S. continues to increase, so does the strain on the healthcare industry. And young doctors, residents, nurses, and medical students are steeling their resolve to help coronavirus patients who need them.
